article_title: Anthem Gains Obamacare Customers And Sees Profits, Expansion Ahead

article_metadata.description: Anthem said it plans to remain in 14 states selling individual plans under the Affordable Care Act with potential for expansion after it completes its merger with Cigna
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
